# Override the API base URL for local development. Default: https://api.btcmap.org
# Option 1 — Vite dev proxy (client-side + SSR load functions via event.fetch):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=/btcmap-api-proxy
# Option 2 — Direct (works everywhere including SSR axios/global-fetch):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
# See vite.config.ts for the proxy config and README.md for setup instructions.
